      <title>由于担心 RSV 疫苗功效下降，Moderna 股价下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/moderna-shares-slide-longer-term-data-shows-quick-fall-rsv-vaccine-efficacy-2024-02-09/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Moderna 周五股价下跌 7%，此前华尔街分析师对其实验性呼吸道合胞病毒 (RSV) 疫苗与葛兰素史克 (GSK) 和辉瑞 (Pfizer) 的竞争对手疫苗相比，其实验性呼吸道合胞病毒 (RSV) 疫苗功效下降更快表示担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/moderna-shares-slide-longer-term-data-shows-quick-fall-rsv-vaccine-efficacy-2024-02-09/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 09 Feb 2024 15:28:51 GMT</pubDate>
